}

docs {
  # Get Single Disease

  Retrieves detailed information for a specific disease by its name.

  ## Path Parameters

  - `name` (string, required): The name of the disease (case-insensitive)
    - Example: `diabetes`, `Diabetes`, or `DIABETES` all work

  ## Success Response (200 OK)

  ```json
  {
    "status": "success",
    "message": "Disease retrieved successfully",
    "data": {
      "name": "Diabetes",
      "image": "https://example.com/diabetes.jpg",
      "description": "A chronic condition that affects how your body processes blood sugar (glucose)",
      "symptoms": [
        "Increased thirst",
        "Frequent urination",
        "Extreme fatigue",
        "Blurred vision",
        "Slow-healing sores"
      ],
      "precautions": [
        "Monitor blood sugar regularly",
        "Maintain a healthy diet",
        "Exercise regularly",
        "Take prescribed medications",
        "Regular check-ups with healthcare provider"
      ]
    }
  }
  ```

  ## Error Response (404 Not Found)

  ```json
  {
    "status": "error",
    "message": "Disease not found"
  }
  ```

  ## Error Response (422 Validation Error)

  ```json
  {
    "status": "error",
    "message": "Validation Error: ✖ Required → at name",
    "errors": {
      "name": ["Required"]
    }
  }
  ```
}
